## Description:

This implementation task aims to enhance the performance and responsiveness of our GN-LLM (Large Language Model) system by incorporating a robust database caching mechanism.
The focus will be on utilizing a database to store queries along with their corresponding answers and references, ensuring quicker retrieval and reduced computational load.


